Im not trying to be a rebel, here. All im saying is i dont want myself to be happy if that's who my future is with. Some guy who isnt into the same music. My music..is my life. It truly is. Some people use this as an extreme form of "i really like music". When  I say it..i mean it with all of my heart. My music is most of what keeps me sane, besides memories of my dad and ethan. But...if it werent for music i wouldnt have made it through the last part of my dad's life and i wouldnt have met ethan. When thoughts of my dads death came to mind..whatd i do? i turned on music or wrote songs! howd i meet mr.ethan? at his band's 1st show!

I guess its weird that i would rather not be happy than be with some guys with weird interests in music, but since music is my life..what do i talk to him about? Who do i go to shows with? What happens when he buys me a kanye west (sp?!) CD? i'll freak out.

I've got some pics but i'll let you guys see those later. On sunday we went to the mall. No hot topic but it's alright..they had an inland ocean and spencers and watnot. <3 Their spencers was h-u-g-e! so it was yummi to hangout there. Some guy sed i had a nice butt? ahah. Yeah he was hawt...lip ring and he had the same tigers[shoes] that ethan does. Hm...but of course he wasnt as beautiful as my lover<3 hehe.

So we came home, watched those movies i told you about, and i called ethan. The next day i went to my kickass mema's[moms mom] who is totally awesome<3 We just went there and i slept. The next day we went to the mall[different one] i kinda forgot what it was called. [o0ops hehe] and some guy gave me his number and wrote it on the back of a subway business card? hahah. i was like hmmm riiiiiight. He was rly hawt though. He kinda had the same hair as i did but thats okay bc ethan kind of does too. Actually if you, seriously, think about it, mine, ethan and joey's hair are completely different. Just bc we all "spike" it in the back..doesnt make it the same. Girls who all have long hair, dont look alike, do they?! no. lol okay..sorry

*back on subject* yeah well neway i didnt keep the number. I decided i didnt need it since i already met my luffer. <3 <3 and i have. so it's okay. I gave the number to Ms.Kayla who's giving it to her boyfriend to call him i guess for idk why? lol. so on wednesday we did some vintage shopping. I only found ONE thing<//3 in 3 diff shops. gRr lyk whoa. neway, we came home and i watched little black book, and garden state. They're both effing adorable. I suggest u go and rent/buy them...NOW. <3 Neway so thursday i basically drove alllllllllllllllllllllll day. ew. Eventually, the driving was worth it bc i got home. HECK YES.

i got to sleep in my own bed<3 yummii it was funnnnn i have a bruise on my head. ow. i miss ethan but i get to seeeee him 2morrow!!<3<3<3<3 ahhhhhhhhhhhhhhh. yay! mall and movies...2morrow. yeah i think movies. not sure though. Then ethan's coming over<3 *muah*
